            <h1 class="highwire-cite-title" id="page-title">UK must act to stem brain drain of scientists, MPs say</h1>    
    <span class='highwire-cite-journal'>BMJ</span>
    <span class='highwire-cite-published-year'>2016</span>;
    <span class='highwire-cite-volume-issue'>355</span>
    <span class='highwire-cite-doi'> doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1136/bmj.i6193">https://doi.org/10.1136/bmj.i6193</a></span>
    <span class='highwire-cite-date'>(Published 18 November 2016)</span>
  <span class='highwire-cite-article-as'>
    Cite this as: <span
